    <section class="article-info">
      <div class="article-content">
        <main class="article article-body text-justify">
          <p>Why does Sound ID lower the overall volume of my desktop? <br>I'm loving the sound profile, but the lower volume is making me consider just un-installing it. <br>All levels are at Max. and it's at a barely acceptable level when playing back media. <br>Surely you're going to fix this...</p>
        </main>

      </div>
    </section>

