                <section class="comment-body"><p>Hey Dylan,<br><br>There could be a few things attributing to this!<br>We generally lower the output slightly depending on what headphones you are using to avoid distortion that could be caused by the boosts in certain frequencies.<br><br>It has also come to our attention that there might be a volume logic issue on some systems. This problem is currently being investigated by our devs and hopefully will be fixed soon.</p></section>
