                    <span title="Kārlis Stenders">
                      
                        Kārlis Stenders
                      
                    </span>

                    <span class="comment-published">
                      <time datetime="2021-11-12T14:59:53Z" title="2021-11-12T14:59:53Z" data-datetime="calendar">November 12, 2021 14:59</time>
                      
                        (Edited <time datetime="2021-11-13T16:37:55Z" title="2021-11-13T16:37:55Z" data-datetime="relative" class="comment-publised">November 13, 2021 16:37</time>)
                      
                    </span>
                  </div>

                  

                  
                </div>

                <section class="comment-body"><p>Hi Brayden, </p>
<p> </p>
<p>Can you elaborate on what are the missing features that are in Reference 4 and not in SoundID Reference? To clarify - yes, there are actually a couple of things that were cut in SoundID Reference for the launch, like, for example, the X-Curve, and the B&amp;K 1974 Speaker targets. Those have since been added back. Also, the Tilt/Bass boost feature is also still missing in SoundID Reference due to some technical issues, but that will also be brought back in the near future :)</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Here's the full list of new features in SoundID Reference:</p>
<p> </p>
<ul>
<li>
<strong><a href="https://sonarworks.com/support/soundid-reference/360003040080-Using-SoundID-Reference/360005379680-Using-SoundID-Reference-app/360020200640" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Custom Target</a></strong> - fine-tune the target curve with a built-in parametric EQ</li>
<li>
<a href="https://sonarworks.com/support/soundid-reference/360003040080-Using-SoundID-Reference/360005379680-Using-SoundID-Reference-app/360020200680" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><strong>Translation Check</strong></a> - check your mix on different devices to see how their music translates outside the studio</li>
<li>
<strong><a href="https://www.sonarworks.com/support/soundid-reference/360003040080-Using%20SoundID%20Reference/360005379680-Using%20SoundID%20Reference/4408352005906" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><em>For listening</em> profiles</a></strong> - support for earbuds and in-ear headphones with 147+ new models</li>
<li>
<strong><a href="https://sonarworks.com/support/soundid-reference/360003040080-Using-SoundID-Reference/360005379680-Using-SoundID-Reference-app/360020245899" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">New Drivers</a></strong> - new WASAPI and ASIO drivers</li>
<li>
<strong><a href="https://www.sonarworks.com/support/soundid-reference/360003040080-Using-SoundID-Reference/360005433680-Using-SoundID-Reference-DAW-plugin/4409282196370-VST3-support-in-SoundID-Reference-WIN-" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">VST3 support </a></strong>- VST3 plugin is now available for both Mac and Windows</li>
<li>
<strong><a href="https://www.sonarworks.com/support/soundid-reference/360003040080-Using%20SoundID%20Reference/360005433680-Using%20SoundID%20Reference/4404699938578" target="_self" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Presets in SoundID Reference DAW plugin</a></strong> - create and save presets right in the SoundID Reference plugin</li>
<li>
<strong><a href="https://sonarworks.com/support/soundid-reference/360003040080-Using-SoundID-Reference/360005379680-Using-SoundID-Reference-app/360020200600" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Configuration Flow</a></strong> - control your configuration from output to preset</li>
<li>
<strong><a href="https://sonarworks.com/support/soundid-reference/360003040080-Using-SoundID-Reference/360005379680-Using-SoundID-Reference-app/360020200820" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">L/R channel switch</a></strong> - swap channels to hear an audio track in a different way you're used to</li>
<li>
<strong><a href="https://www.sonarworks.com/support/soundid-reference/360003040080-Using-SoundID-Reference/360005418959-FAQ/4409766538642" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Mono mode</a></strong> - switch from Stereo output to Mono output to make better decisions while mixing</li>
<li>
<strong><a href="https://www.sonarworks.com/support/soundid-reference/360003040080-Using%20SoundID%20Reference/360005418959-Using%20SoundID%20Reference/4409760126098" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Dark theme</a></strong> - now available in the plugin format too</li>
<li>
<strong><a href="https://www.sonarworks.com/support/soundid-reference/360003040080-Using-SoundID-Reference/360005418959-FAQ/4409760126098" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Appearance sync</a></strong> - allows syncing the light/dark theme with OS setting</li>
<li>
<strong><a href="/hc/en-us/articles/360020200780" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Responsive design</a></strong> - resize the app window size to your needs with a swing of a mouse</li>
<li>
<strong><a href="/hc/en-us/articles/360020200780" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">UI Zooming</a></strong> - adjust the magnification level of the UI elements</li>
<li>
<strong><a href="/hc/en-us/articles/360020200780" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Compact View</a></strong> - simplify your GUI view</li>
<li>
<strong><a href="https://www.sonarworks.com/support/soundid-reference/360003040080-Using%20SoundID%20Reference/360005433680-Using%20SoundID%20Reference/4408064696338-Zoom-feature-in-SoundID-Reference-plugin" target="_self" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Zoom feature in SoundID Reference plugin</a></strong> - adjust the magnification level of the plugin window</li>
<li>
<strong><a href="https://sonarworks.com/support/soundid-reference/360003040080-Using-SoundID-Reference/360005379680-Using-SoundID-Reference-app/360020200840" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">New headphone selection wizard</a></strong> - revamped selection wizard with the option for models with multiple modes</li>
<li>
<strong><a href="https://sonarworks.com/support/soundid-reference/360003040080-Using-SoundID-Reference/360005379680-Using-SoundID-Reference-app/360020200520" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Log-in based authorization and license management</a></strong> - create your SoundID Reference account to log-in and register the product</li>
<li>
<strong><a href="https://sonarworks.com/support/soundid-reference/360003040080-Using-SoundID-Reference/360005379680-Using-SoundID-Reference-app/360020200800" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Hints and tooltips</a></strong> - get to know the tool you're working with</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p>There is a long list of other smaller additions, but the main features are listed in a nutshell above. You can expect the same continuous improvements and new features being released with upcoming SoundID Reference software updates too, just like it was with Reference 4.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>It would be great to hear your thoughts on what is still missing in order for the upgrade to be worthwhile. Thank you!</p></section>
              </div>

